These are Puzzles for 6x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-1::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, jet-ski, car, tram
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, peach, plum, radish
City: edinburgh, venice, paris, hamburg
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, journalist, manager, tramcher
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, dubstep, funk, r&b
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, pony, bird, fish
 1. the tramcher is on the far right##1
 2. the person driving the car is the fan of classical##1
 3. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the fan of funk##1
 4. the person eating plum is on the left of the person eating peach##1
 5. the person driving the tram is the person eating radish##1
 6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
 7. the manager is between the owner of the hedgehog and the fan of r&b##2
 8. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
 9. the fan of classical is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
10. the owner of the hedgehog is between the manager and the person eating radish##2
11. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
12. the tramcher is the person traveling to hamburg##1
13. the fan of funk is between the fan of dubstep and the person traveling to paris##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |      4      |
| Transport      | tram        | jet-ski       | car  | ship |
| Food          | radish     | plum         | peach     | broccoli    |
| City         | venice  | edinburgh      | paris   | hamburg     |
| Job           | journalist | entrepreneur | manager   | tramcher     |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep    | funk         | classical | r&b         |
| Pet         | fish     | hedgehog     | pony  | bird       |

