.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, fanta, soy-milk, sprite
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, aristoff, bongani, havana
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, thriller, time-travel, western
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, electronic, folk, gospel
4 different pets are kept: lizard, hedgehog, turtle, mouse
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, dahlia, balloon-flower, daisy
 1. the owner of the hedgehog is between the bongani-smoker and the person who growsamaryllis##2
 2. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 3. the havana-smoker is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
 4. the owner of the hedgehog is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person who growsballoon-flower##2
 5. the fan of disco is the person drinking fanta##1
 6. the fan of folk is on the far right##1
 7. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
 8. the person who growsballoon-flower is between the person watching action movies and the havana-smoker##2
 9. the person watching thriller movies is the havana-smoker##1
10. the chaman-smoker is on the far left##1
11. the fan of disco is the person watching time-travel movies##1
12. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
13. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
14. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Beverage      | sprite    | fanta       | soy-milk   | almond-milk |
| Cigar         | chaman     | bongani   | havana    | aristoff  |
