The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, family, scientific
4 different pets are kept: bird, horse, chinchilla, fish
There are 4 different favourite colors: azure, blue, emerald, mauve
 1. the townhouse house is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the owner of the chinchilla##2
 2. the palace house is on the left of the designer##1
 3. the person who likes blue is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
 4. the ranch-style house is on the left of the townhouse house##1
 5. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
 6. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the cottage house##1
 7. the scientist is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
 8. the person who likes emerald is the person watching scientific movies##1
 9. the person who likes azure is between the scientist and the person who's hobby is azured-games##2
10. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
11. the person who's hobby is azured-games is on the left of the person who likes azure##1
12. the software-developer is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
13. the palace house is the palace house##1
14. the person who's hobby is gardening is the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |         2          |     3      |     4     |
