 8. the spanish is the person driving the van##1
 9. the person driving the ship is the egyptian##1
10. the person driving the van is the person who's birthday is in august##1
11. the fan of metal is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
12. the spanish is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
